snippet.title: LISA - DREAM feat. Kentaro Sakaguchi (Official Short Film MV)
snippet.description:
LISA’s debut album, ‘Alter Ego’ is out now. Listen here: https://lisa.lnk.to/AlterEgo   
Shop vinyl, CDs, photobooks and more: https://lnk.to/LisaStore 

Follow LISA: 
http://www.instagram.com/lalalalisa_m
https://www.tiktok.com/@lalalalisa_m
https://www.youtube.com/@lalalalisa_m

Follow WeAreLLOUD:
http://www.instagram.com/wearelloud
https://www.tiktok.com/@wearelloud
http://www.facebook.com/wearelloud
https://www.youtube.com/@wearelloud/videos

Lyrics:
I’ve been thinking 
That I got no idea what you’re thinking 
Are you happy? Are you sad?
Are you always gonna hate me for that night in Tokyo? 
When it ended 
I kinda hoped that it’d be open ended
But you never looked back 
Well I guess you can’t hold on to something once you let it go 
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I guess that I’m taking what I can get 
‘Cause I don’t get nothing new from your friends 
If you got the harder side of the break 
Then why is it harder for me to take 
There’s so much I might never get to say, ay
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I-I-I know it’s only in my mind
Playing three nights on the stereo
Like a movie scene, DiCaprio 
Oh l-I-I put my make up on just to fall asleep
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is something we’ll never be
It’s bittersweet
Can we be friends at least

snippet.description:
KEREN 1000%!! Dapatkan Badge 500 HARI dari RUSA Anomali 👑🦌👑 | 99 Nights in the Forest Indonesia

Nama Game : 99 Nights in the Forest
Link Game : https://www.roblox.com/games/79546208627805

🔰 Sekarang kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat VOICE di Room Santuy yang ada di Discord. Jadwal ga tentu, tapi biasanya kalau sore sekitar jam 15.30 - 16.30 WIB. Baca lagi bagian bawah biar kalian benar-benar mengerti 🗿

Sebelum JOIN, tolong baca ini ya 🙏😁
✅ Izin sama orang tua & tanya boleh ga install dan main Discord? Btw, discord punya aturan kalau mau buat akun mesti umur 13+
✅ PENTING!! Ikut MABAR atau RECORD mungkin agak susah karena ramai yang tungguin bang Hayo, sedangkan game Roblox server-nya terbatas
✅ Record juga GA SELALU MABAR  karena beberapa game ga boleh rusuh & mesti diatur sebaik mungkin
✅ Kalau mau record, bang Hayo kabarin lewat voice "Room Santuy" di discord
✅ Ga bisa ADD karena sudah full. Satu-satunya solusi adalah FOLLOW akun Roblox bang Hayo dan nanti kalian bisa JOIN bang Hayo main. Lalu, kalau bang Hayo lagi AFK atau SERVER sudah penuh, teman-teman ga bisa join ya
✅ Kadang bang Hayo harus pakai LINK PRIVATE SERVER biar record-nya lebih lancar. Kirim link-nya di Discord & untuk cara JOIN baca di cara-ikut-record yang ada di Discord
✅ Baca PERATURAN GROUP & PERTANYAAN UMUM  di Discord untuk kepentingan bersama
✅ Di group ini kalian juga bisa mencari KAWAN yang mungkin cocok sama kalian dan bisa main bareng. Ga perlu fokus sama bang Hayo saja karena bang Hayo ga mampu standby 24 jam
✅ Mohon pengertiannya kalau ga berhasil JOIN bang Hayo karena server sudah FULL & sistemnya siapa cepat dia masuk dulu

🔰 Bang, kenapa ga bisa chat di Discord?
Untuk menjadi MEMBER di Discord, teman-teman harus tulis username Roblox yang AKTIF di nama-roblox & baca bagian peraturan-server

🔰 Bang, CARA JOIN gimana ya?
Bang Hayo sudah jelasin secara lengkap di Discord. Cari saja di channel cara-ikut-record biar kalian paham. Lalu, akun yang umurnya kurang dari 13 tahun akan agak sulit buat join karena peraturan terbaru Roblox

And the reason is you

A side of me you didn't know
A reason for all that I do
And the reason is you
